snippet.title: Still Working On It | skate.
snippet.description:
We told you we’re back, and we’re still working on it - but it’s time for you to see what we’ve been up to. It’s still early, but we want to get this right and that means we want you to be a part of it.

Become a skate. insider at http://skate.game/insider for a chance to play, provide feedback and help shape the future of skate.

Web: http://skate.game 
Twitter: http://twitter.com/skateEA 
Instagram: http://instagram.com/skateEA 
Discord: http://discord.gg/skateEA
